# .env.example
#
# WHAT THIS FILE IS: a TEMPLATE showing which secret values JARVIS needs.
# It contains NO real secrets and IS safe to commit to git.
#
# HOW TO USE IT:
#   1. Copy this file and rename the copy to exactly ".env" (no extension)
#   2. Replace the placeholder below with your real Gemini API key
#   3. Never share your real .env file or commit it to git — it's already
#      listed in .gitignore, so a normal `git add .` will skip it safely.
#
# WHERE TO GET A FREE API KEY (no credit card required):
#   https://aistudio.google.com/apikey  -> Sign in -> Create API key

GEMINI_API_KEY=your-api-key-goes-here
